	<div class="alphaBackground"></div>
	<header>
		<h1>Blog</h1>
		<p>The writing of Alex Cash. Dangerous thoughts from a dangerous man.</p>
		<nav>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="../"><i class="icon-home"></i><span> Home</span></a></li>
